    "        \"potential_issue\": \"Contains 'hate speech' but is discussing the problem\"\n",
    "    },\n",
    "    {\n",
    "        \"text\": \"You're completely wrong about everything.\",\n",
    "        \"category\": \"Strong Disagreement\",\n",
